version 2.1.1    2019-1-11

- C++11 support, replace raw pointers with smart pointers, replace atomic operations with thread-safe synchronization
- Add memory allocation and release tracking interface




version 2.0.3    2018-12-12

- Add interface to stop all download tasks
- Add interface to stop all tasks when one download fails




