- Fix progress calculation bug in multi-threaded download mode
- Add qt creator project files
- Optimize networktool project




version 2.0.1    2018-9-18

- Rename project to QtMultiThreadNetwork
- Add multi-threaded download file interface
- Fix thread-safety issues in multi-threaded processing
- Add HTTP/HTTPS DELETE/HEAD request method interface




